            <lg xml:id="TK1105">
<l>vēṭṭa poḻuti ṉavaiyavai pōlumē </l>
<l>tōḷtāḻ katuppiṉā ṭōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The shoulders of her whose locks are adorned with flowers delight me as if they were the very sweets I have desired (to get).</l>
